---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
    description: "Learn about Gurdwara Singh Sabha Richardson and its services.",
    title: "About - Gurdwara Singh Sabha Richardson",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
    <div class="mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">About Gurdwara Singh Sabha Richardson</h1>
        
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Who Are We?</h2>
            
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                Since its founding in 1984, Gurdwara Singh Sabha Richardson has been a vibrant Sikh community center located in Richardson, Texas. It serves as a spiritual, educational, and cultural hub for Sikhs in the Dallas-Fort Worth metroplex. Our mission is to promote the teachings of Sikhi and foster a sense of unity and service among the community.
            </p>

            <p class="text-lg mb-6">
                The Gurdwara offers a variety of services and facilities to support the community, including:
            </p>

            <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-4">
                <li>
                    <strong>Sikhi School:</strong> Weekly classes for children and adults to learn about Sikh history, Gurbani, and Punjabi language.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Langar Kitchen:</strong> A fully operational kitchen providing free meals to all visitors, embodying the Sikh principle of selfless service.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Recreational Facilities:</strong> Spaces for sports, fitness, and community gatherings to promote health and well-being.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- Image Section -->
<div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Gallery</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <img 
            src="/assets/images/MainHall.jpg" 
            alt="Gurdwara Main Hall" 
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
        />
        <img 
            src="/assets/images/Langar.jpg" 
            alt="Langar Hall" 
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
        />
        <img 
            src="/assets/images/MainHallScreen.jpg" 
            alt="Community Event" 
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
        />
    </div>
</div>

        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-accent-one pl-4 italic my-6">
            "ਵਿਚਿ ਦੁਨੀਆ ਸੇਵ ਕਮਾਈਐ ॥<br/>
            ਤਾ ਦਰਗਹ ਬੈਸਣੁ ਪਾਈਐ ॥"
            <br/>
            <span class="text-sm mt-2 block">
                "In the midst of this world, do seva, and you shall be given a place of honor in the Court of the Lord." - Sri Guru Granth Sahib Ji
            </span>
        </blockquote>

        <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Visit Us</h2>
    <p class="text-lg mb-4">
        Gurdwara Singh Sabha Richardson is located at:
    </p>
    <address class="text-lg font-semibold">
        1201 Abrams Rd, Richardson, TX 75081
    </address>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4">
        We welcome everyone to join us for prayers, langar, and community events. Come and experience the spirit of Sikhi and seva.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4">
        For more information, feel free to <a href="/contact" class="text-accent-one underline">Contact Us</a>.
    </p>
</div>
    </div>
</PageLayout>